section.heading: Short title.
section.text: This subchapter may be cited as the “Interagency Collaboration and Services Integration Commission Establishment Act of 2007”.

annotations.annotation: Applicability: Section 508 of Law 17-9 provided that this title this subchapter shall apply upon Congressional enactment of Title IX. Congress enacted the provisions of Title IX in Pub. L. 110-33, approved June 1, 2007.
